maven-nexus-helm-setup/
├── maven/
│   └── pom.xml
├── nexus/
│   └── docker-compose.yml
├── helm/
│   └── mychart/
│       ├── Chart.yaml
│       ├── templates/
│       │   └── deployment.yaml
├── README.md


1. Maven Setup (maven/pom.xml)
<project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0"
         xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
         xsi:schemaLocation="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0
                             http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd">
    <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>

    <groupId>com.example</groupId>
    <artifactId>demo</artifactId>
    <version>1.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
    <packaging>jar</packaging>

    <name>demo</name>
    <url>http://maven.apache.org</url>

    <dependencies>
        <!-- Example dependency -->
        <dependency>
            <groupId>junit</groupId>
            <artifactId>junit</artifactId>
            <version>4.13.2</version>
            <scope>test</scope>
        </dependency>
    </dependencies>
</project>

2. Nexus Setup (nexus/docker-compose.yml)
version: '3'
services:
  nexus:
    image: sonatype/nexus3
    container_name: nexus
    ports:
      - "8081:8081"
    volumes:
      - nexus-data:/nexus-data
    restart: unless-stopped

volumes:
  nexus-data:


 Nexus will be available at: http://localhost:8081

 3. Helm Setup (helm/mychart/)
helm/mychart/Chart.yaml
apiVersion: v2
name: mychart
description: A Helm chart for Kubernetes
type: application
version: 0.1.0
appVersion: "1.0"

helm/mychart/templates/deployment.yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: {{ .Release.Name }}-app
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: {{ .Release.Name }}-app
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: {{ .Release.Name }}-app
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: myapp
          image: nginx
          ports:
            - containerPort: 80

4. README.md
# Maven + Nexus + Helm Setup

This repository includes setup files for:

- Maven (Java project)
- Nexus (Docker-based artifact repository)
- Helm (Sample chart)

---

##  Maven

Path: `maven/pom.xml`

Build with:
```bash
cd maven
mvn clean install

 Nexus

Path: nexus/docker-compose.yml

Run with:

cd nexus
docker-compose up -d


Access: http://localhost:8081

 Helm

Path: helm/mychart

Install with:

cd helm/mychart
helm install myrelease .


---

##  5. GitHub Commands (Shell)

You can use these to set up the project and push to GitHub.

### **Create the folder and files**
```bash
mkdir -p maven-nexus-helm-setup/{maven,nexus,helm/mychart/templates}
cd maven-nexus-helm-setup






Create files using cat or copy-paste the content above into:

maven/pom.xml

nexus/docker-compose.yml

helm/mychart/Chart.yaml

helm/mychart/templates/deployment.yaml

README.md

Git Commands to Push to GitHub
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit: Maven, Nexus, and Helm setup"
# Create GitHub repo using CLI
gh repo create maven-nexus-helm-setup --public --source=. --remote=origin --push


Or manually create a GitHub repo and push:

git remote add origin https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/maven-nexus-helm-setup.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
